    "phases": [
      {
        "id": "phase-warm-up",
        "name": "warm-up",
        "duration": 5,
        "items": [
          {
            "type": "canvas",
            "canvasData": "{}",
            "teacherNotes": "### Why Learn Cyrillic?\n\nUkrainian uses the Cyrillic alphabet - 33 letters total. Good news: many look familiar! This module covers 18 letters you can learn quickly.\n\nThe key insight: some letters LOOK like English but make DIFFERENT sounds. We call these \"False Friends\" - they'll trick you if you're not careful!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "phase-presentation",
        "name": "presentation",
        "duration": 15,
        "items": [
          {
            "type": "canvas",
            "canvasData": "{}",
            "teacherNotes": "### Group 1: True Friends (7 letters)\n\nThese letters look AND sound like their Latin equivalents:\n\n| Letter | Sound | Example |\n|--------|-------|---------|\n| А а | A (as in \"father\") | мАмА |\n| Е е | E (as in \"bet\") | мЕтро |\n| І і | I (as in \"machine\") | таксІ |\n| О о | O (as in \"hot\") | фОтО |\n| К к | K | Кафе |\n| М м | M | Мама |\n| Т т | T | Тато |\n\nTrust these! They work exactly as you'd expect."
          },
          {
            "type": "canvas",
            "canvasData": "{}",
            "teacherNotes": "Group 2: False Friends (6 letters)\n\nDANGER! These look Latin but sound completely different:\n\n| Letter | Looks like | Actually sounds like |\n|--------|------------|---------------------|\n| В в | B | V (as in \"van\") |\n| Н н | H | N (as in \"no\") |\n| Р р | P | R (rolled, as in Spanish) |\n| С с | C | S (as in \"sun\") |\n| У у | Y | U (as in \"flute\") |\n| Х х | X | KH (as in German \"Bach\") |\n\nMemorize these! They cause the most confusion for beginners."
          },
          {
            "type": "canvas",
            "canvasData": "{}",
            "teacherNotes": "Group 3: New But Easy (5 letters)\n\nThese don't exist in Latin but are straightforward:\n\n| Letter | Sound | Memory tip |\n|--------|-------|------------|\n| Б б | B | Belly with a belt |\n| Д д | D | Like a house |\n| З з | Z | Like the number 3 |\n| Л л | L | Like a tent |\n| П п | P | Like a doorway/portal |\n| Ф ф | F | Like a person with arms out |"
          },
          {
            "type": "activity",
            "activityId": "act-uk-A1-01-matchup"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "phase-practice",
        "name": "practice",
        "duration": 15,
        "items": [
          {
            "type": "canvas",
            "canvasData": "{}",
            "teacherNotes": "### Reading Strategy\n\nWhen you see a Cyrillic word:\n1. Go letter by letter\n2. Watch for False Friends (В=V, Н=N, Р=R, С=S, У=U, Х=KH)\n3. Sound it out slowly\n4. Many words are cognates - they'll sound familiar!"
          },
          {
            "type": "canvas",
            "canvasData": "{}",
            "teacherNotes": "Try These Words\n\nSound out each word. Most are international words you'll recognize:\n\nБАНК → B-A-N-K → bank\nПАРК → P-A-R-K → park\nМЕТРО → M-E-T-R-O → metro\nКАФЕ → K-A-F-E → café"
          },
          {
            "type": "activity",
            "activityId": "act-uk-A1-01-quiz"
          },
          {
            "type": "activity",
            "activityId": "act-uk-A1-01-groupsort"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "phase-production",
        "name": "production",
        "duration": 10,
        "items": [
          {
            "type": "canvas",
            "canvasData": "{}",
            "teacherNotes": "### Reading Challenge\n\nRead these words without looking at transliteration:\n\n1. МАМА\n2. ТАТО\n3. СТУДЕНТ\n4. ФУТБОЛ\n5. МУЗИКА"
          },
          {
            "type": "canvas",
            "canvasData": "{}",
            "teacherNotes": "False Friend Drill\n\nRemember: П = P, Р = R, В = V, Н = N, С = S, Х = KH\n\nRead these tricky words:\n- СУПЕРМАРКЕТ (supermarket)\n- РЕСТОРАН (restaurant)\n- ПАСПОРТ (passport)"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
